<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚就是讓人期待已久的萬聖節了！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然距離活動開始還有一些時間，<delay20 />
但我已經開始感到熱血沸騰了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於……<delay8 />今天就是萬聖節了！<delay frames="40" />
我已經做好萬全準備了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來只等活動開始的信號啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">終於到了萬聖節這一天！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會拿出真本事來的，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最好也全力以赴喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">萬聖節馬上就要開始了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最好也趕快提前待命，<delay8 />
免得慢人一步喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />距離萬聖節開始的時間越來越近，<delay20 />
差不多該做最後確認了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要謹慎再謹慎才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再一下子就5點了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到萬聖節即將開始，<delay20 />
我就興奮到無法冷靜，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這個月有萬聖節，<delay20 />
所以在島上<delay8 />不時可以看見
南瓜裝飾啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣<delay8 />感受著島上的氣氛<delay20 />
漸漸進入萬聖節模式，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺也還不壞，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每當在島上<delay8 />看到南瓜裝飾時，<delay20 />
內心總會掀起一陣漣漪啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道……<delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待活動嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算只是南瓜裝飾，<delay20 />只要達到這種數量，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來就是很壯觀啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有這麼多的話，<delay8 />萬聖節當天的氣氛
一定會很熱烈，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />目所能及的地方，<delay8 />
都是滿滿的<delay20 />南瓜裝飾啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣萬聖節當天的氣氛，
應該會相當熱烈<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過這收拾起來應該很麻煩吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>